rformance during the specified window.", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on the metrics data collected for the anomaly period, I'll now perform a comprehensive analysis to identify significant anomalies. Here's my initial scan of the trace data:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in client_error_ratio and error_ratio metrics (p99 change ratio: 2.0)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 26.46, error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 26.46\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated client_error_ratio and error_ratio metrics (p99 change ratio: 2.0)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 19.47, error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 19.47\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice pods (adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2)\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage spike and response time degradation across all adservice pods\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage increased from 0.0 to 0.6 (median change ratio: 2.0), rrt_max increased significantly for adservice-1 from 42246.0 to 130879.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Response time maximum (rrt_max) spike indicating performance degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99 increased from 7239.52 to 47772.1 (p99 change ratio: 1.4736)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory availability reduction and potential resource pressure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased from 13109424128.0 to 7922741248.0 (median change ratio: 0.4932)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-